Description:
Low maintenance, top location!

In a top location close to Newcomb and Bellarine shopping centres, sporting facilities, public transport and only 5 minutes from the CBD, this is a lovely opportunity to own a low maintenance unit. The living room is comfortable and provides a warm welcoming area to relax. Through the large laundry is a hassle-free, fully fenced private courtyard to take entertaining outdoors. The unit has the added benefit of solar panels and parking for one car. Presented to please, this unit is one you'll be proud to call home.

Description:
"Endless Potential on a Huge Corner Block"
Set on approximately 753 square metres the home features 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 with built in robes, with the third being optional bedroom or an extra living space.
The home also offers a study zone with plenty of cupboard space. The family bathroom includes bath, shower and single vanity. The open plan living and kitchen area while functional provides plenty of opportunity to make it into something of your own. The large laundry area with ample storage space and separate toilet leads out to the generous backyard with extra-large double garage and a covered courtyard along the side of the home. Extra features include reverse cycle heating and cooling and wood fire in the living area.
This substantial home will suit the saavy purchaser. With some renovations this home offers an affordable opportunity to enter the market, or as an investor add some TLC and reap a great rental return.
Take advantage of the corner block aspect and develop or subdivided STCA.
Outstanding location and situated within walking distance to public transport, schools and shops including Newcomb Centro shopping centre, Splashdown, St. Albans football ground as well as plenty of parks and walking tracks close by. What a great way to end the year by purchasing a home to make into something special whether it be for yourself or an addition to your investment portfolio.
Home Owner: We have loved the location and enjoyed watching the growth over of the years'.
Roncon Real Estate - An Agency like no other!

The large open plan living area with wood heater and breakfast bar flow out onto the rear deck and outdoor living that looks over the low maintenance spacious rear yard.

Hardwood floors, gas heating and air-conditioning complete this wonderful opportunity to avoid paying rent any longer.

Description:
A Stylish Home Loaded with Features, Space and Comfort
If you have been looking for that home with a little extra something, then this one just may be it. Situated on a massive 836m2 block (approx.) with a 21 metre frontage with secure rear yard that has side access for your trailer or boat. This home was built by Italian bricklayers 27 years ago and built to stand the test of time. With renovations and updates throughout, the home offers the astute buyer a stylish and comfortable lifestyle.
The new kitchen in this home will be the envy of your friends and comes complete with stone tops, high gloss vinyl wrap doors, stainless steel build-in wall oven and cooktop with heaps of storage for the biggest of families and opens out to the large dining area. The lounge room has beautiful wall recesses fitted with down lights, and is set up for the perfect cinema experience. Offering 4 generous bedrooms with BIR, all robes fitted with draws, shelving and heaps of hanging space and polished board will make this home a haven for the growing family.
Offering a large central bathroom with a sumptuous corner spa bath with a separate toilet. The home has wall to wall built in robes to solve all of your storage problems.
With an approx. return of $330- $350 per week.
Additional Features: keyless front entry, 2 car remote garages, with side access, large zinc shed, ducted gas heating, split system. Close to schools, public transport, major shops, and five minutes from the CBD.
